OL,3,CThird man arrested after tonne of
OL,4,Ccocaine found hidden in banana cargo
OL,6,FA third man has been charged after
OL,7,Falmost a tonne of cocaine was found
OL,8,Fhidden in a shipping container of
OL,9,Fbananas.
OL,11,FThe consignment, which had come from
OL,12,FNicaragua via Panama, was discovered
OL,13,Fat Southampton dock by Border Force
OL,14,Fofficials acting alongside the
OL,15,FNational Crime Agency.
OL,17,F943kg of the Class A drug was found
OL,18,Fwith a street value of around #75m.
OL,20,FTwo men were charged in connection
OL,21,Fwith the seizure on 18th of March.
