OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774807892
OL,3,CThird man arrested after tonne of
OL,4,Ccocaine found hidden in banana cargo
OL,6,FNow, a third man, Joshua Berry, 28, of
OL,7,FAnna Lane in Bransgore, Hampshire, has
OL,8,Fappeared in court charged with
OL,9,Fimporting a Class A drug and the
OL,10,Fproduction of Class B drugs.
OL,12,FAll three men have been remanded in
OL,13,Fcustody and are next expected to
OL,14,Fappear before Southampton Crown Court
OL,15,Fon 17 April.
OL,17,FSpeaking in relation to the seizure,
OL,18,FNCA Branch Commander Saju Sasikumar
OL,19,Fsaid: "This is a massive amount of
OL,20,Fcocaine which was destined for the
OL,21,Fstreets of the UK.
OL,26,@{D@GOU
