OL,3,CThird man arrested after tonne of
OL,4,Ccocaine found hidden in banana cargo
OL,6,F"The supply of Class A drugs badly
OL,7,Fdamages society by bringing violence
OL,8,Fand addiction to our communities.
OL,10,F"Seizing these drugs deprives the
OL,11,Fcrime group behind the importation of
OL,12,Fhuge profits that cannot be ploughed
OL,13,Fback into further offending."
